source.name: 2012 Proposed Budget - Expenditures Allowance by Budget Control Level (BCL)
source.description: This data comes directly from Attachment A to the 2012 Budget Adoption Ordinance. This data reflects all appropriations (by budget control level) included in the 2012 Proposed Budget.
